Package com.fincons.rabbitmq.publisher

Provide a set of classes to implement a client Publisher and Publisher's Event data entity.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
EventFactory This interface defines methods to create Event objects to be published.
Publisher This interface represents a producer of events collected by the RabbitMQ Server.
 

Class Summary
BasicEventFactory Provides the default implementation of EventFactory.
BasicPublisher Provides the default implementation of Publisher.
